title: (Thurs Part 1) The Elder vs. Millennial CHAMPIONSHIP + REJECTED SEGMENTS!
itunes:title: (Thurs Part 1) The Elder vs. Millennial CHAMPIONSHIP + REJECTED SEGMENTS!
description:
Eddie and Morgan2 face off in the championship round of Elder vs. Millennial. The winner takes all in this round! Bobby shares a list of segments that were sent in by members of the show but didn't' get used. He explains why in a round of REJECTED SEGMENTS. Amy also gives an update after hosting an event for adoptive and foster moms. She also reveals how many bottles of wine ended up being used to settle Bobby and Eddie’s over/under bet.
